msgctxt "816"
msgid "Tatsu-ya Noodles"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60_Tatsu-ya Noodles"
msgid "Once a customer places an order, Kiryu must cook the noodles to the requested consistency. They will gradually soften as they cook.\\r\n"
"Serve the ramen by pressing the indicated button when the Consistency Gauge matches the order."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72_Tatsu-ya Noodles"
msgid "The pace of customer orders increases in stages as you successfully fill them. You won't proceed to the next stage if you botch too many.\\r\n"
"Up to one hundred customers will place orders. Aim for the title of Ramen King!"
msgstr ""

